            <svg width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><path d="M20.49 15a9 9 0 1 1-.08-5.96"/></svg>
            تحديث
